1. Spawn it.
Spawn or jump one or more creatures in(to) this area. You can use Precious to copy a PC if needed.

2. Customise it. 
You can change stats, add equipment, modify appearance, whatever you like.

Click on one of the slot PLCs to safe the creature(s) in the corresponding DMS creature slot. You can see what you have saved in your DMS settings page in Admin Tools.
